angrydd: angrydd (Falling blocks game)
angrydd:
angrydd: In Angry, Drunken Dwarves (ADD), you are an angry, drunken dwarf.
angrydd: Why are you so angry? Who knows. But you've decided to take your
angrydd: aggression out on other dwarves, by dropping gems on their heads.
angrydd: Lots of gems. ADD is a member of the classic "falling blocks" puzzle
angrydd: game family, similar to the Capcom game Puzzle Fighter. The goal of
angrydd: the game is to build large gems by matching up colors, then break
angrydd: them, raining more gems down onto your opponent. The first person
angrydd: whose field fills up, loses. http://www.sacredchao.net/~piman/angrydd/
